data.description: This well cared for home sits on 3.9 ACRES in Gardendale.  NO HOA.  Zoned for the new Warrior Elementary, North Jefferson and Mortimer Jordan.  Country living at its finest with room to spread out but still close to all the conveniences and entertainment of Gardendale.  5 minutes from I-65.  List of upgrades include:  New Lights, Farm Fence & Mailbox Outside; Exterior Painted 2020; New Landscaping; New Hardwood Floors; Updated Master (Granite) and Guest Bath; Updated Kitchen with Butcher Block Counters, Large Pantry; Large Laundry/Mud Room added with Plumbing for Pet Shower; New Hardware and Ceiling Fans in Every Room; Fresh Paint Upstairs; Replaced Section of Warn Driveway; New Hardwood Flooring in Main Living Areas and MORE; 3D Virtual Tour Available Schedule Your Showing Today!
